com.langtoun.oastypes

Interface OASStringType

  • All Superinterfaces:
    OASType
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OASStringTypeImpl

    public interface OASStringType
extends OASType
    Public interface for OpenAPI specification object types. Objects of this type are derived from YAML like this: 
    
   type: string
